IT'S A MIXED BAG.
蛮复杂的

189
00:08:51,298 --> 00:08:53,632
A LOT OF VERY GOOD-INTENTIONED PEOPLE
很多善意的人

190
00:08:53,634 --> 00:08:55,734
DEALING WITH SOME DIFFICULT CIRCUMSTANCES.
在处理各种难题

191
00:08:55,736 --> 00:08:57,802
YOU GET OVER THERE VERY OFTEN?
你经常到那儿去吗？
YEAH.
是的

192
