AN AFTERSCHOOL FILMMAKING CLASS.
一个课外电影制作班

214
00:09:44,251 --> 00:09:47,652
IT'S WITH A BUNCH OF KIDS, AND THEY'RE REALLY GREAT
给一群很棒的孩子上课

215
00:09:47,654 --> 00:09:50,322
AND SO SMART AND, UH, JUST CREATIVE.
他们很聪明，很有创造力

216
00:09:50,324 --> 00:09:51,856
