AT LEAST YOU HAVE A SEXY ROOMMATE.
至少你有一个性感的室友

294
00:12:50,303 --> 00:12:53,238
FELICIA? I FIND HER A BIT TERRIFYING.
你是说Felicia吗？ 我觉得她有点可怕

295
