……啥

303
00:13:07,420 --> 00:13:09,053
HEY.
SHIRIN.

304
00:13:09,055 --> 00:13:10,355
I'M NOT SAYING YOU SHOULDN'T DO IT.
我不是说你不该这么做

305
00:13:10,357 --> 00:13:12,157
IT'S JUST...
只是

306
