你到底想干什么

317
00:13:30,177 --> 00:13:31,876
YOU DON'T KNOW WHAT A COOL BROOKLYN LOFT LOOKS LIKE.
你根本不知道一个布鲁克林房间有多酷

318
00:13:31,878 --> 00:13:33,044
I JUST DON'T UNDERSTAND
我是真的不懂

319
00:13:33,046 --> 00:13:34,412
WHY YOU LEFT YOUR OLD APARTMENT.
为什么你要搬家

320
00:13:34,414 --> 00:13:36,981
THE NEIGHBORHOOD WAS SO MUCH BETTER.
原来那些邻居都很棒

321
00:13:36,983 --> 00:13:38,817
IT GOT TOO EXPENSIVE.
那里太贵了

322
00:13:38,819 --> 00:13:40,218
WE WOULD HAVE HELPED YOU.
我们会资助你啊

323
00:13:40,220 --> 00:13:42,153
THIS IS MY NEW HOME, AND I LOVE IT.
这里是我新家，而且我很喜欢

324
00:13:42,155 --> 00:13:43,321
OKAY.
好吧

325
00:13:43,323 --> 00:13:45,590
ALI, COME. HELP ME IN THE KITCHEN.
Ali，到厨房来帮忙

326
