SHE HAS NO GOALS OR ASPIRATIONS.
她没有目标没有动力

336
00:14:10,150 --> 00:14:11,516
SHE TAKES NOTHING SERIOUSLY.
她对任何事都不在意

337
00:14:11,518 --> 00:14:12,617
